1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,379
Google made a new AI that can write computer code.

2
00:00:03,679 --> 00:00:08,439
This AI is so good, it writes code better than people do.

3
00:00:08,739 --> 00:00:13,879
The AI learns from lots of code and can fix bugs or make new programs.

4
00:00:14,179 --> 00:00:17,179
For example, it can create a game where you guess a number.

5
00:00:17,479 --> 00:00:23,839
Humans can write code too, but this AI does it faster and with fewer mistakes.

6
00:00:24,139 --> 00:00:27,839
This could help people build apps and websites more easily.

7
00:00:28,139 --> 00:00:31,959
Technology like this is changing how we create things.

8
00:00:32,259 --> 00:00:35,939
Try learning to code yourself to see how awesome it is!

